The Wait Until Event element is updated with the ability to wait until a specific link in an email or SMS is clicked.

Where: This feature is available in Lightning Experience for Salesforce Enterprise and Unlimited editions with Marketing Cloud Growth edition.

How: In Flow Builder, add the Wait Until Event element to the canvas. If the selected email or SMS contains links, you can select which specific link to wait for.
